Hey Guys   Your problem will be like jason said more than likely at the 
trottle body on the engine. Be real careful adding springs to the cable on any bus 
I have seen this cause the pivot under the gas petal to get bent. Wasn't made 
to have too much force put on it. Later and have fun  Mark Dearing  Salem 
Import Service Salem Va
